column5: Any reports on Wabaskang Lake as far as fishing and water levels? Thanks and be safe and lucky out there.
How about it? anybody been up to report? Later, Jay
We will be up there June 23-30; so hope there is a report prior to leaving MQT, MI
Jim and Julie's website reports water levels coming up slowly with a ways to go. We are there June 23-30 as well ... hoping for cooler temps and no mayflies.

If you want fishing reports for Wabaskang, see Tall Pines Blog, Jim and Julie's Camp News, Peffley's is on Facebook and also has a blog, and then you can also look at Wine Lake Camp Blog. These provide weekly updates normally on Sunday/Mondays, after the past week is over.
